%% Encounter happy path
%% Source: Strategy Overview flow + Architecture APIs + Q&A UCs
sequenceDiagram
  actor Provider
  participant EHR as EHR Chart
  participant SMART as SMART App browser
  participant FHIR as EHR FHIR API
  participant API as Mesmerize Platform API
  participant Dev as Exam Room Device

  Provider->>EHR: Launch Mesmerize
  EHR->>SMART: SMART launch iss+launch
  SMART->>FHIR: OAuth + read Patient/Condition/Encounter
  SMART->>API: Create session ICD-10 + deviceGroup only
  API-->>SMART: sessionId
  SMART->>API: Recommend content
  API-->>SMART: Ranked content
  Provider->>SMART: Select device + push
  SMART->>API: POST /devices/:id/command
  API->>Dev: Socket.io show_content / biodigital
  Dev-->>API: Engagement events
  API-->>SMART: Engagement + billing suggestions
  Provider->>SMART: Review / approve evidence
  SMART->>FHIR: DocumentReference write optional
  Note over API: No patient identifiers stored
  Note over SMART: FHIR token never leaves browser
